{"tid":1980080,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(支共又辣火頭) 華設西沙南沙兩區　擴南海霸權","createTime":"2020-04-20T00:49:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T06:02:30.000Z","uid":6604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0e535daba9cc4eae571f2c983239cfddedd3413b","tid":1980080,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T00:49:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200419/APCTIXG2BGWYGCIAIHXTE6KMZM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200419%2FAPCTIXG2BGWYGCIAIHXTE6KMZM%2F&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPkXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=2d29bad2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200419%2FAPCTIXG2BGWYGCIAIHXTE6KMZM%2F&h=7660e883\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200419/APCTIXG2BGWYGCIAIHXTE6KMZM/</a><br />\n<br />\n中國民政部昨發公告表示，國務院近日批准海南省三沙市設立西沙、南沙兩區。這是2012年7月中國宣佈成立三沙市管轄南海及南沙群島、引發越南外交抗議及排華行動後，中方在南海又一重大動作，或再招越南等對南海有主權爭議國家的反對。<br />\n<br />\n公告指，新成立的三沙市西沙區，管轄西沙群島島礁及海域，代管中沙群島島礁及海域，區人民政府駐永興島；三沙市南沙區管轄南沙群島島礁及海域，區人民政府駐永暑礁。此意味中方填海填出的永暑礁，將有中國政府派駐機構進駐。永暑礁原是南沙中部一個岩礁，沒於海面下。2015年中方填海後成為南沙三大人工島之一，與美濟礁和渚碧礁齊名。<br />\n<br />\n目前永暑礁面積2.8平方公里，建有3,000米跑道的機場和5,000噸級的碼頭。永暑礁填海造陸尚未完成，該島真正礁盤全長26公里，寬7.6公里，總面積達108平方公里，最終建成的永暑島預計將擁有62平方公里陸域面積（略小於香港島），及35.5平方公里內港。未來將成中國於南海軍事戰略要地。<br />\n<br />\n2012年7月24日中國宣佈成立三沙市，屬海南省管轄地級市，市政府駐地西沙永興島，轄西沙、中沙、南沙群島島礁及其海域，總面積200多萬平方公里。事件惹對南海有主權爭議的越南強烈抗議，越南國內隨後掀起新一波反華潮。"},{"pid":"361b1160da529a89ae155271615e7a4101af59dd","tid":1980080,"uid":289946,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T00:51:55.000Z","msg":"其實有冇人知雜大大諗緊乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n霸左南海其他船行唔到，好難唔打仗"},{"pid":"d3cebac5130e2ea26aa68ff842283faeb9bca5d6","tid":1980080,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T00:52:45.000Z","msg":"睇嚟有人即將被維尼流放<br />\n放去個島仔做區長cls"},{"pid":"f2d039656738c4134de12c3c6e739a7a6ab2ccbd","tid":1980080,"uid":303917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T00:57:50.000Z","msg":"其實係咪已經係宣戰行為？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a160bd89d37659bb08fbeb9e1954fc57af769f57","tid":1980080,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f2d039656738c4134de12c3c6e739a7a6ab2ccbd","tid":1980080,"uid":303917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T00:57:50.000Z","msg":"其實係咪已經係宣戰行為？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T01:24:54.000Z","msg":"中共：干涉中國內政"},{"pid":"0eb3536ca26b7a9acd70c448e74ba98b1cafc59a","tid":1980080,"uid":24443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T01:25:51.000Z","msg":"打佢老尾臭西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cd45aecd4d142e9adcec2e7dfb1b90160f74b5c","tid":1980080,"uid":144001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T02:03:32.000Z","msg":"睇黎唔打下 小支支係學唔識教訓"},{"pid":"251594224787151c3af89c1cc3c90a28b59a8992","tid":1980080,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T02:04:20.000Z","msg":"諗住周圍起火頭<br />\n搏有一個跑出? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37c56c718262beb57c03659d25e23e5028d99767","tid":1980080,"uid":91028,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T02:05:39.000Z","msg":"其實CCP係咪真係覺得武肺搞到歐美不行鳥，中國形勢大大大好呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f29754b4625846e4837d173de15397a2890c8753","tid":1980080,"uid":224882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T02:05:59.000Z","msg":"<del>辣</del><span style=\"color: red;\">㷫</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmo